  "prompt": "What is the definition of dude?",
  "response": "The term \"dude\" originally referred to a man who is properly dressed or stylish, often associated with urban sophistication. Over time, its meaning has evolved and expanded. Today, \"dude\" is commonly used in informal contexts to refer to any person, regardless of gender, and is often used as a casual term of address among friends. It can also convey a sense of camaraderie or informality. In contemporary slang, it can denote someone who is laid-back or nonchalant. The usage and connotation can vary based on region and social context.",
